✅ Day 74 – Problem: Remove K Digits
Problem

Given a numeric string and integer k, remove exactly k digits to form the smallest possible number.

Approach

Traverse digits and maintain a monotonic increasing stack

Remove previous digits if they are larger than current and k > 0

If removals remain, delete from the end

Strip leading zeros

Return "0" if result is empty

Complexity
Aspect	Value
Time	O(N)
Space	O(N)
Language	Java ☕
